alan (0.4.0~pre1-1) emily; urgency=low

  * Added icon support. Requires Openbox 3.5.0 and enable_icons = True
    in config.
  * core/config.py: return False instead of "false" if an option isn't
    on the configuration file.
  * core/config.py: added load_config() function, loads a configuration.
    replaces the configuration loading process in alan-gentree.py
  * alan-show-extension: add configuration support. Use ids instead of
    real extension name in command-line argument.
  * ext/*: icon support, except for music.
  * core/: added extension library.
  * ext/*: adapted to match the inclusion of the new alan.core.extension.
    WARNING: THIS BREAKS ALL OLDER EXTENSIONS!
    Your extension should now be into the class Extension (derivative
    of alan.core.extension.Extension), definition run.
    .
    menu should become self.menu!
  * ext/xdgmenu: support for configuration variable split_menu.
    If True, the categories will be loaded when the user will
    pass its cursor on.
    Default is False.
  * core/config: ConfigRead: if option value is "True" or "False",
    return relative booleans instead of string.
  * debian/* and setup.cfg:
    - Ship alan to /usr/share/alan instead of /usr/lib/alan
  * tree.conf: added icons, split_menu = False.

 -- Eugenio Paolantonio (g7) <me@medesimo.eu>  Sat, 27 Aug 2011 12:55:28 +0200

